                <mxCell id="legend-notes" value="DDD Patterns Used:&#xa;• Bounded Contexts: Customer, Account, Transaction, Payment, Fraud, Notification, Audit, Reconciliation&#xa;• Aggregates: Each context has aggregate roots that ensure consistency&#xa;• Domain Events: Async communication between contexts via Event Bus&#xa;• Shared Kernel: Common value objects (Money, Currency, DateTime)&#xa;• Anti-Corruption Layer: Payment Gateway isolates external systems (ITMX, NPMS)" style="text;html=1;fontSize=9;align=left;spacing=5;whiteSpace=wrap;shadow=1;textShadow=1;" parent="legend" vertex="1">
